Following the bombings, an attorney for Russell released a statement saying she was cooperating with the investigation.

'As a mother, a sister, a daughter, a wife, Katie deeply mourns the pain and loss to innocent victims, students, law enforcement officers, families and our community,' the attorney, Miriam Weizenbaum, said in the statement.

